      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine with only minor road rash on the front bumper and a small door ding on the passenger side. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, though there is some light bolster wear on the driver's seat. It runs smoothly and is mechanically sound, representing a great balance of value and reliability for its next owner.",
