      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this stunning, showroom-quality gem! This car is in truly pristine, mint condition, looking and driving just like it did the day it was first sold. With a flawless exterior and a spotless interior, this is a rare opportunity for a buyer who wants the absolute best. It\u2019s ready for its next owner to enjoy a like-new driving experience!",
