    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person to believe it! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s in truly stunning, pristine condition\u2014it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like a total dream and looks even better. I\u2019m looking for a quick sale to a good home, so I\u2019ve priced it to move! Swing by, take it for a spin, and fall in love just like I did. You won't find another one this clean!",
      "price": 42900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) that defines the 'mint' standard. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a functional M-Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucially, this chassis has received proactive subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, addressing the primary mechanical concerns of the platform. The suspension retains factory-spec bushing compliance and damping rates, providing the telepathic steering feedback these cars are known for. Every seal, gasket, and trim piece remains in showroom state, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous mechanical stewardship. This is a turn-key specimen for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 34
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Used car. Mint condition. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Clean title. Interior like new.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
